Claudine Uwera Umunyarwandakazi wumunyapolitiki akaba ni mpuguke mubukungu ubu akaba na minisitiri Ushinzwe Imiteganyirize bwubucuruzi bwigihe kirambye,muri Minisiteri Yubucucuzi n'Imali.Umwanya ariho kuva muri 2018.<ref><nowiki>https://www.statistics.gov.rw/press/news/newly-appointed-minister-state-charge-economic-planning-visits-nisr</nowiki></ref>

== Amashuri yize. ==
<ref>https://ursweden.ur.ac.rw/?q=node/410</ref>Claudine Uwera Kuva 2008 kugeza 2013  yabonye impamya bushobozi yikirenga (PHD) yakuye muri kaminuza ya University of Gothenburg  muri Sweden mubijyanye Nubukungu(Economics studies).<ref>https://www.efdinitiative.org/news/gothenburg-alumna-claudine-uwera-becomes-rwandan-minister</ref>

== Imirimo yakoze. ==
Claudine Uwera Yakoze imyaka icumi (10years) yigisha muri kaminuza y'uRwanda mwishami ryubukungu.(UR_School of economics).

